sequenceDiagram
  participant W as Writer
  participant F as Stream file<br/>(page cache)
  participant R as Reader
  participant S as Socket

  W->>F: append (advances tail)
  F-->>R: wake live readers

  R->>F: GET ?offset (byte range)
  Note over F: wire bytes already on disk —<br/>nothing to decode or reframe
  F->>S: sendfile (zero-copy)
  Note over F,S: one copy serves every live reader.<br/>History streamed in fixed windows.
